node.text: So, a few years ago I had a big time agent who really believed in the Teacher Misery books and went to all the major publishers with it. She sent me their responses, some of which I've shared with you here, with MY responses. These are the very small group of gatekeepers who hold the keys to getting books into stores and this is what they think of truth telling. (I messed up the publishers. Slide 3 was Chronicle and 4 was St. Martin's Press. Do I have the balls to tag them?)
